     <body>
     <div type="dedication">
   <pb facs="2"/>
   <head>To the right Worshipfull, Sir Christopher Heydon, C.T. wisheth aeternall fruition of all felicitie.</head>
   <l>THou, thou that art the Muses <hi>Adonie,</hi>
   </l>
   <l>Their Pyramis, adorner of their mount,</l>
   <l>Thou Christalizer of their <hi>Castalie,</hi>
   </l>
   <l>Thou Lillian-rose, sprung from the horse-foote fount,</l>
   <l>To thee, Artes Patron, Champion to the highest,</l>
   <l>That giuest the Sunne a fairer radiance,</l>
   <l>To thee <hi>Musophilus,</hi> that still appliest</l>
   <l>Thy sacred soule, to be Trueths esperance.</l>
   <l>To thee (this Epinyctall register,</l>
   <l>Rasde out by <hi>Eos</hi> rayes) I write to thee.</l>
   <l>To thee (this hoarie <hi>Hiems,</hi> kill'd by <hi>Ver</hi>:)</l>
   <l>To thee (this metamorphosde Tragoedie)</l>
   <l>To thee, I write my Apotheosie:</l>
   <l>
      <hi>Moecenas,</hi> strengthen my Tyrocinie.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>
         <hi>Your Worships euer,</hi>
         <hi>Cyrill Turner.</hi>
      </signed>
   </closer>
</div>
